snippet: Liver trouble killed a giant panda cub last month, less than a week after its surprise birth at the National Zoo.
abstract: National Zoo official says liver trouble killed giant panda cub, less than week after its surprise birth in mid-September.
lead_paragraph: Liver trouble killed a giant panda cub last month, less than a week after its surprise birth at the National Zoo.
